text: Gutenberg Alejandro Martínez Ocamica (born 29 August 1950) is a Chilean politician who served as President of the Chamber of Deputies and as a member of the Chamber of Deputies, representing District 21 of Santiago. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:People from Santiago Category:Presidents of the Chamber of Deputies of Chile Category:University of Chile alumni
title: Gutenberg Martínez
